blog.name: wrathofconpics
blog.title: WRATH OF CON pics
blog.description:
JH and Spooky dump their con pics here (our cosplay). Drop us a line if you recognize anyone!

We also post our photos on Flickr and Facebook with no Tumblr usernames. If you don't want your picture posted there or here, just contact us.

Browse by con or by category: Animation | Anime / Manga | Books | Comics | Miscellaneous | Movies | Television | Video Games | Homestuck | non-Homestuck Webcomics

Too many tags on a post can break things a little, so use use the search box to be sure you've found everything in a tag (example: Ivalice).
